FactoryController

Floor-level factory/shop automatization control software.

MODBUS realtime network & devices controller. 
Hi-level task-centric parallel execution scenaries. 
MRP/ERP integration.

Features

*    MODBUS network controller (default)
*    Plugable interface for other industrial networks
*    Set of default devices (reference design)
*    Task execution scenaries
*    Workcell-centric parallel task execution
*    Realime (with preemptive OS kernel)

